id: pm-csv-017m
title: Command handlers threw plain Error (no exitCode) → runtime double-invocation
description: "csv import/export threw plain Error without numeric exitCode; pm's runCommandHandler then falls through its unhandled path and re-invokes the handler a second time, exiting with a generic code. Added dependency-free CommandError mirroring SDK EXIT_CODE; missing-arg=2, missing-file=3 (ENOENT), other failures=1; single invocation."
type: Issue
status: closed
priority: 2
tags: []
created_at: "2026-06-01T10:16:11.676Z"
updated_at: "2026-06-01T10:16:11.976Z"
author: codex
parent: pm-csv-z5f8
close_reason: "Fixed: CommandError carries exitCode. Verified full functionality — round-trip import/export works, error paths exit 2/3/1 with single invocation."
body: ""
